<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a5May1937"><font color="red">5 May 1937</font> <i>NLJL</i> (from G. Wren Howard to Paul L&eacute;on): I have just received the first fruits of our reader&apos;s comparison of the John Lane ULYSSES with &hellip; Odyssey Press. He has made a note of certain points which he is unable himself to settle, and about which he would like to have Mr Joyce&apos;s precise instructions. I enclose a list of these queries. </div>
